fields.name: Contract
fields.description: You can order the service of writing a contract on your terms with the help of our qualified lawyers. The contract is drawn up very quickly and inexpensively, which will save your time.
fields.summary: Order a contract based on your terms

fields.name: Appeal
fields.description: Thanks to our professional lawyers, you can appeal a negative decision on your case. With many years of experience, our lawyers will help you resolve the case in your favor.
fields.summary: Here you can purchase service to appeal your decision

fields.name: Property Division
fields.description: With the help of our lawyers, you will be able to make a property division, a list of the property that you want to divide with your partner, as well as calculate the share that will be transferred to you after the division itself.
fields.summary: Divide your property easily and quickly

fields.name: Application
fields.description: With our help, you can quickly fill out an application, which in turn will speed up the process of reviewing your case in the government agency to which the application is sent.
fields.summary: Here you can order the service for filling out the application

fields.name: Notarius Publicus
fields.description: With the help of a notary, you can get confirmation of your foreign documents that require a state seal. By ordering this service, you will simplify the process of preparing documents.
fields.summary: Notarize any document in the shortest possible time

fields.name: Letter
fields.description: With our help you can write a warning letter to your opponent with whom you are arguing. A well-written letter in 90% prevents further lawsuits that can be very expensive for the losing party.
fields.summary: Here you can buy out service for write letter to your opponent

fields.name: Testament
fields.description: We will help you to draw up a correctly and legally correct online will (testament) based on the points you want to include. A correctly drawn up testament prevents further litigation, which often arise between close people after the death of the person who left the will.
fields.summary: Make a testament securely and correctly

fields.title: Order Success
fields.question: What happens after I pay for the service?
fields.answer: After receiving the payment, our lawyers contact you by the phone number you left and we agree with you on a video conference via any messenger convenient for you, for example, Zoom or Meet.

fields.title: Right Of Withdrawal
fields.question: What happens if I regret my purchase?
fields.answer: We offer a 100% satisfaction guarantee, which means you have the option to cancel your purchase and get your money back within 14 days of receiving the product. If you want to cancel a purchase, just contact us by email or phone.

fields.title: Personal Data Sharing
fields.question: Does LawForYou share my personal data with others?
fields.answer: All information you provide in connection with the preparation of your legal documents is treated confidentially and of course we do not share your information with others. See our Privacy Policy for more information.

fields.title: Personal Data Safety
fields.question: Is it safe to provide my personal data to LawForYou?
fields.answer: Information you provide to LawForYou is transmitted via an encrypted SSL (Secure Socket Layer) connection and is protected from the outside world. All information you provide in connection with the production of your legal documents is treated confidentially. See our Privacy Policy for more information.

fields.title: Payment Safety
fields.question: Is it safe to pay with LawForYou?
fields.answer:
When you pay with a payment card at LawForYou, all your entered card data is encrypted/coded when it is forwarded to the payment intermediary. Thus, only the payment intermediary can read them. Neither LawForYou nor anyone else has access to your data.
For the transactions, LawForYou uses an approved SSL (Secure Socket Layer) solution to encrypt/encode your entered card data. Encryption with SSL is used in most online stores.
An amount greater than what you have authorized at the time of purchase can never be deducted from your account.

fields.title: Free Of Charge Contact
fields.question: Does it cost anything to contact LawForYou?
fields.answer: The initial contact with LawForYou is of course free of charge.

fields.title: Hiring Us For The Review Of Documents
fields.question: Can you be hired to review just one agreement?
fields.answer: Yes, it's going well. We also offer ongoing advice with a fixed price per hour and billed monthly.

fields.title: Our Location
fields.question: In which locations are you located?
fields.answer: We have offices in central Stockholm and have the opportunity to sit on site with customers in Gothenburg and Malmö. As a starting point, contact and advice will otherwise take place remotely - all for increased accessibility and the opportunity to offer smart legal services to more people.
